cs.FL, cs.DS, cs.LO, cs.IT, cs.CC

Reasoning: 
- cs.FL (Formal Languages and Automata Theory) is the most likely category as the paper deals with regular languages and finite automata. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is also likely as the paper discusses multiplication and order dependence. 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is relevant as the paper deals with recognizing ultimately periodic sets. 
- cs.IT (Information Theory) may be relevant as the paper discusses translation and multiplication by constants. 
- cs.CC (Computational Complexity) may be relevant as the paper deals with recognizing sets of natural numbers.
